# Tech Stack

## App Platform
- Expo SDK 52
- React Native
- TypeScript

## Navigation & UI
- Expo Router
- React Navigation (tabs/stacks)
- Unistyles v3 (Tailwind-like styling)
- Burnt (toast notifications)

## State & Data
- TinyBase (latest, with SQLite persistence)
- Zustand (only if needed)
- Expo SQLite
- SecureStore for secrets

## Auth
- Clerk (Expo-compatible, JWT sessions)

## AI / LLM
- Whisper (voice-to-text for logging)
- Custom prompt system fed from `llms.txt`
- Workout suggestion API tools

## Monitoring & Monetization
- Sentry (crash reporting)
- RevenueCat (via `react-native-purchases`)

## OTA & Deploy
- EAS Updates
